      <title>亚马逊推迟发射柯伊伯宽带卫星计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/amazon-delays-launch-of-project-kuiper-broadband-satellites</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司表示，预计将于今年第四季度发射首批太空互联网卫星，此前该公司曾表示最早将于上半年发射。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/amazon-delays-launch-of-project-kuiper-broadband-satellites</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 18:06:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
