      <title>Nvidia 零售热潮引发 ETF 世界巨变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/nvidia-retail-craze-unleashes-wild-moves-in-the-world-of-etfs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从快速致富计划的增长到成为业绩优异的决定性因素，英伟达公司最新的市场过山车式波动警示我们，这家人工智能芯片制造商在规模 9.2 万亿美元的美国 ETF 体系中的重要性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/nvidia-retail-craze-unleashes-wild-moves-in-the-world-of-etfs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 14:00:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
